title: Leaves from the journal of our life in the Highlands, from 1848 to 1861 :
author: Victoria
snippet: Going up Cairn Ture we looked down uponLock Canter, a small loch above Lock Callater,very wild and dark.

title: Leaves from the journal of our life in the Highlands, from 1848 to 1861 :
author: Victoria
snippet: In a little more than two hours we wereat Lock Callater — the road was very bad indeedas we approached the loch, where our ponieswere waiting for us.
